overview:
Jessica Rios is the cofounder and Clinical Director for iCouch, Inc., a mental health and wellness technology company. She manages the counselor recruitment, retention for iCouch.me, iCouch’s flagship online counseling platform.

Jessica Rios has been a licensed counselor since 2004. She has advanced degrees in both clinical psychology and education. She has been a private practice counselor for expat clients in the Shanghai area since 2009.

Prior to China, Jessica worked retail corporate management in Guadalajara Mexico. She is an expert on technology usage in psychological care, especially in tele health applications.
